##########
# Win 10 / Server 2016 / Server 2019 Initial Setup Script - zomg turbo preset
# Source: https://github.com/Disassembler0/Win10-Initial-Setup-Script
# Usage:
# From elevated shell:
# powershell.exe -NoProfile -ExecutionPolicy Bypass -File Win10.ps1 -include Win10.psm1 -preset Turbo.preset

##########

### Require administrator privileges ###
RequireAdmin

### Privacy Tweaks ###
DisableWiFiSense
DisableAppSuggestions
EnableLocation
DisableAdvertisingID
DisableWebSearch
DisableCortana
EnableDiagTrack

# Restrict Windows Update P2P delivery optimization to computers in local network - Default since 1703
SetP2PUpdateLocal

### Security Tweaks ###
DisableSMBServer
EnableFirewall
EnableDefender
SetUACHigh
DisableAutoplay
DisableAutorun

### Network Tweaks ###
DisableRemoteAssistance

### Service Tweaks ###
EnableFastStartup
EnableUpdateMSProducts
DisableUpdateRestart
DisableMaintenanceWakeUp
EnableUpdateAutoDownload
DisableAutoplay
DisableAutorun

### UI Tweaks ###
EnableTitleBarColor
DisableLockScreen
DisableLockScreenBlur
ShowTaskManagerDetails
ShowSmallTaskbarIcons
SetTaskbarCombineAlways
HideTaskbarPeopleIcon
ShowTrayIcons
HideRecentlyAddedApps
HideNetworkFromLockScreen
HideShutdownFromLockScreen
SetSoundSchemeNone
DisableStartupSound

# Adjusts visual effects for performance - Disables animations, transparency etc. but leaves font smoothing and miniatures enabled
SetVisualFXPerformance

SetSoundSchemeNone
DisableStartupSound

### Explorer UI Tweaks ###
ShowKnownExtensions
ShowHiddenFiles
DisableThumbsDBOnNetwork
DisableThumbnails

### Application Tweaks ###
UninstallOneDrive
UninstallThirdPartyBloat
UninstallMsftBloat
DisableAdobeFlash
DisableXboxFeatures
InstallLinuxSubsystem
InstallHyperV
UninstallXPSPrinter
RemoveFaxPrinter

### Unpinning ###
UnpinStartMenuTiles
UnpinTaskbarIcons

